{"tid":348003,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[工程撚]兩年BS Consulant經驗知識水平要去到咩程度？","createTime":"2017-08-05T10:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T12:00:09.000Z","uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6855579edfa7b55b0ae454ca38770aec0ac45b90","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"做左兩年都係覺得自己範範半桶水都冇，D知識好鬆散，想專一範但公司做野又唔到我揀。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以講下AE, E, SE 大概要做到咩程度先合理，例如：<br />\n<br />\nAE: Drafts, 畫圖，drawing skill, run project?<br />\nE: Plan system routing, feasibility study, system selecting, run project?<br />\nSE: 已經冇頭緒"},{"pid":"10ce8de3966fbba909f33084f3ed8c9cb8edefe4","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"前排有機會跟senior出去開會，好多時聽唔明佢地講乜，technical唔講，好多文件野都唔知，返去搵資料先知，例如WSD 報開工，掛電錶etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正常黎講大概做幾耐先識自動波去run project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a441661a29915cc6a833017675becf6b9e3cc4","tid":348003,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"你做sub 仔一年咩都識 不過係被人屌住先識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682660e2421951838246ff4a35e2ff67097a878a","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做sub 仔一年咩都識 不過係被人屌住先識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n見senior 出去開會，真係乜撚問題都有，文件程序野，technical (風火水電）乜問題都有，SE要識呢D，E又要玩到咩程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b9a9a6d3d00c682483ce677f4eb7bd932c007a","tid":348003,"uid":73613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f6a5b89627d80e7690313ae9f0106979f12e904","tid":348003,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"你依家先知bs係垃圾唔等駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753ee34e87770f2f7de3dd92f8f6e0c1d4b2793e","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩年經驗等同main con做4年或者sub con做2-3年經驗<br />\n睇個人造化,如果肯工餘時間睇多d書同參考過住pj<br />\n基本上風火水電都可以答到哂問題,好多有用既comments都寫到出黎</blockquote><br />\n但d 問題真係估佢唔到，可以好detail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f117089f1a8b6f3f52ec35f619f287578c7e1080","tid":348003,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"做十仔𡃁仔好似多D機會睇哂所有文件 程序野"},{"pid":"8e8239620949abc8170923a47e0200368947a172","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做十仔𡃁仔好似多D機會睇哂所有文件 程序野</blockquote><br />\n但係design/code方面technical又怕唔夠"},{"pid":"c48b76b1906afc824925568d9022f444998482db","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f5710ce1594d4be319980d1b5993f5efaeaa60","tid":348003,"uid":106243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:29:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左兩年都係覺得自己範範半桶水都冇，D知識好鬆散，想專一範但公司做野又唔到我揀。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以講下AE, E, SE 大概要做到咩程度先合理，例如：<br />\n<br />\nAE: Drafts, 畫圖，drawing skill, run project?<br />\nE: Plan system routing, feasibility study, system selecting, run project?<br />\nSE: 已經冇頭緒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你果兩年係consultant係專做一範，咁做左兩年應該對以下items 有基本概念同可以半獨立咁做呢D tesk：&nbsp;<br />\n1)Load calculation&nbsp;<br />\n2)System selection&nbsp;<br />\n3)Preparation of tender drawings&nbsp;<br />\n4)Tender document analysis&nbsp;<br />\n5)Authority submission&nbsp;<br />\n6)Detail design for construction stage&nbsp;<br />\n7)Approval of submission&nbsp;<br />\n8)睇T&amp;C&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n如果你果兩年係做哂四範，咁都起碼對果四範既系統有基本了解。"},{"pid":"38772ce6ce4d17414eb7ab196664f6364ed77480","tid":348003,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:47:40.000Z","msg":"得閒報d學會既短期course or seminar<br />\n好多時會請左唔少行內專家講下d基本野或者行業新趨勢<br />\n學到唔少野"},{"pid":"12a4232da1d5a6842d20a7136be90fb5fe46ff03","tid":348003,"uid":36113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T09:58:29.000Z","msg":"其實consultant公司中一單project大約搵到幾多錢？<br />\n例如私人發展話商住宅項目/政府公屋村分別lump sum幾多？"},{"pid":"c967e82b878ade1fd54bf19cee6a11820f162bad","tid":348003,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb21b6f5055d4dd5210f5b3da255d99be93b4e6","tid":348003,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c967e82b878ade1fd54bf19cee6a11820f162bad","tid":348003,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T12:00:09.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我工都轉撚埋十世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你條廢人仲咁得閒幫我推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係廢物一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}